      "name": "Pump Pressure-Rise Characteristic Validation",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pump head (pressure rise) was compared against manufacturer-supplied hydraulic performance data across the same 5 operating points to confirm that the flow field solution is physically consistent before hemolysis quantities are extracted.",
